  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Assessing the long-term efficacy, complications, revision rates and final explantation of the
      device
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Longitudinal study with a follow-up of 2 years in patients implanted with the Precision
      neurostimulator.

      This study will describe the characterisrics of the patients, of the implantation and will
      assess the long-term efficacy, complications, revision rates and final explantation of the
      device
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
